’Ł@dd6412011a7346e672d771c0e333f15e3f56ab1f3e1aa929e0e6f94528b1828eŁ‚Title: title: job flush
Path: Examples
Content:
Clear the mailbox of the current job.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> job flush


```
’Ł@3931c7f22855eb2f3ab4f618f254af19c9551e3b4ab6f4906c1b9a56e0addc2aŁĒTitle: title: job flush
Path: Notes
Content:
This command removes all messages in the mailbox of the current job.

If a message is received while this command is executing, it may also be discarded.
